import React from 'react';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom';
import { Row, Col } from 'antd';
ReactDOM.render(
    <Row>
      <Col xs={{ span: 5, offset: 1 }} lg={{ span: 6, offset: 2 }}>
        Col
      </Col>
      <Col xs={{ span: 11, offset: 1 }} lg={{ span: 6, offset: 2 }}>
        Col
      </Col>
      <Col xs={{ span: 5, offset: 1 }} lg={{ span: 6, offset: 2 }}>
        Col
      </Col>
    </Row>,
    mountNode,
  );
